data.description: A fantastic opportunity to secure a 3.75% LOAN!!!  Don't miss out on this amazing property with unlimited potential for expansion. It's being offered at a great price, and with your personal upgrades, you can turn it into your dream home. The sizable backyard boasts leveled terraces, perfect for gardening or creating a serene patio oasis.  Additionally, the property could potentially accommodate an ADU with parking.   This prime location is just a 5 minute drive from the Glen Cove Waterfront Park, offering plenty of outdoor activities and walking trails. The Glen Cove Shopping Center is also conveniently located nearby. With easy access to highways 780 and 80, as well as the Ferry, your commute will be a breeze. Don't let this opportunity pass you by!
